Yobe State Governor, Mai Mala Buni on Sunday received in audience the newly appointed Director General, Great Green Wall Programme, Dr Yusuf Maina Bukar. Dr Bukar who assumed office last week, visited the Governor to express his appreciation for the support given to him. Governor Buni congratulated the new DG and advised him to be dedicated to duty and be a good ambassador of the state. Responding, Dr Bukar assured to put in his very best for the success of the programme and to remain a worthy ambassador of the state. He commended Governor Buni for the support and assured him that he will justify his appointment as Director General of the programme.